{"tid":2275291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關稅華：因選舉政治而帶動的貿易議題可望短期內消除","createTime":"2020-11-07T04:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T00:55:50.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b32a783b10eaa5a1012478f6113941e4de9db6cf","tid":2275291,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:50:06.000Z","msg":"等多四年啦關稅華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n若果無武漢肺炎我都驚美國換總統會縮，而家有肺炎加料，美國佬點會縮呀，歐洲佬都反檯緊啦傻西，加埋參眾兩院比共和黨反cup，你識唔識架傻西<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=411958\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D411958&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuODT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=61434dae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D411958&h=df66c6ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=411958</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華表示，美國大選之後，中美之間因選舉而引發的貿易壁壘，有望短期內解決。他又指，因應歐洲新冠病毒疫情升溫，香港與當地商討旅遊氣泡的進度亦會拖慢。<br />\n<br />\n美國大選之後，中美貿易關係會如何發展？商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華在本台節目《大鳴大放》相信，美國要先處理國內經濟，一些因選舉引發的貿易壁壘，有望短期內消除。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華：「我相信在新政府，無論他是甚麼人也好，他也要處理國內經濟問題，這個經濟問題，包括進出口、不同行業。我認為起碼有一點，隨着選舉結束，有一些因選舉政治而帶動、影響貿易政策的因素，希望能在短期內消除。」<br />\n<br />\n至於港府早前表示，與十一個國家及地區商討旅遊氣泡，邱騰華承認，由於疫情關係，部分國家難以短期內實施。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華：「名單不是固定，這段時間亦有很多國家敲門，我們也留意世界各地會否有，但名單次序不是先到先得，例如有一個很大的因素，該地疫情如何。現時來說，例如歐洲情況似乎不太樂觀，這部分工作可能要拖慢點，但準備工作可以進行。」<br />\n<br />\n至於與新加坡的旅遊氣泡，邱騰華重申，希望首批旅客可於本月內成行。他指本港機場會設專門通道，讓新加坡旅客抵港時進行快速檢測，並研究在機場設化驗室，縮短檢測時間。"},{"pid":"adad156cd7224d78eae24266cfa2714dafb8ff9a","tid":2275291,"uid":270308,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:52:03.000Z","msg":"阿司長咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開心死連登班sleepy Joe fans"},{"pid":"b353e0e5e6e9fc2ed985c4d088a62f66c6d90ba8","tid":2275291,"uid":7369,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:56:07.000Z","msg":"四年前侵侵上台果陣支那人都歡天喜地架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1550446159a6dcf93fdfcbfcc0d58c3fe54d71eb","tid":2275291,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:56:11.000Z","msg":"等多四年啦關稅華"},{"pid":"1a19f5188bae24220f7d35522f4f16bbb85ea7cf","tid":2275291,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:57:48.000Z","msg":"Four more years<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1e31ed3a28cbe6792527646ff1c3629fb96d9f","tid":2275291,"uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T05:00:43.000Z","msg":"坐得呢個位，連西方國家外交政策有持續性都唔知真心on9"},{"pid":"68367c77f0561e597c0c97bc894e60183f46301c","tid":2275291,"uid":2054,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T05:03:07.000Z","msg":"五眼比Trump擺左上台<br />\n而家夾返China Joe抗中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a9797bb467ed4e9bcb203a19b6cd65662a2b5c","tid":2275291,"uid":46500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc1e31ed3a28cbe6792527646ff1c3629fb96d9f","tid":2275291,"uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T05:00:43.000Z","msg":"坐得呢個位，連西方國家外交政策有持續性都唔知真心on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T05:05:41.000Z","msg":"因為哩條撚樣係一朝天子一朝臣嘅受益人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7884bc989e77c38c1620e52ba37cba5cabed7b19","tid":2275291,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T05:06:46.000Z","msg":"如果最後都係Trump當選<